headline: Truist Raises CACI (CACI) Price Target, Highlights Strong Government Contract Growth
summary: CACI International, Inc. (NYSE:CACI) is one of the most undervalued cybersecurity stocks to buy now. On August 8, Truist analyst Tobey Sommer raised the price target for CACI International, Inc. (NYSE:CACI) to $575, up from the previous $550, an implied upside of 16.3% from the current level of $493.99. Sommer kept a Buy rating on the […]
